inlineContent.text: You can use category samples to record sleep data using the

enumeration. Individual samples represent time periods when the user is in bed or asleep. Samples with different values may have overlapping time intervals. For example, when the user is both in bed and asleep, create an in-bed sample and an asleep sample with overlapping times.
